Say '''Pilar''' et kumatlo ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Capiz]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 41,572 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 77.99 sq. km. Sikato et walad unaan ya distrito. Say zip code to et 5804.	
															
